Appliance
The Appliance class is an abstract class of other specific devices.
ApplianceLoader
The ApplianceLoader class is responsible for loading and saving a list of Appliance objects from/to a text file.
ApplianceManager
The ApplianceManager class is responsible for managing a collection of appliances, including displaying a user menu, and processing user requests to check out appliances, find appliances by brand, display appliances by type, and produce a random list of appliances.
Dishwasher
The Dishwasher class represents a specific type of appliance that extends the Appliance class.

The ModernApplianceApp class is the entry point for the appliance management application.
